{"tid":184033,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"十四日布拉格遊","createTime":"2017-04-02T14:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T07:42:23.000Z","uid":27334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c529bc4d74ed520fee1a6a3398061cb81a13be31","tid":184033,"uid":27334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:07:21.000Z","msg":"5月中去十四日獨遊<br />\n首先會去布拉格<br />\n應該會去下vienna或者Budapest，或者BOTH<br />\n想問下時間可以點分配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係Prague會去aeroprague渣下小型飛機，諗緊玩唔玩skydiving<br />\n因為想所有budget控制係10k~12k<br />\n住就搵airbnb<br />\n<br />\n另外仲想問下溝通方面淨係英文會唔會好大障礙，尤其睇牌睇火車站果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為打算巴士/火車去另外兩個城市"},{"pid":"704b7b0f0b35f32b7c7c3651bd5e70dbc1d31434","tid":184033,"uid":27334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:07:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>5月中去十四日獨遊<br />\n首先會去布拉格<br />\n應該會去下vienna或者Budapest，或者BOTH<br />\n想問下<span style=\"color: red;\">日數</span>可以點分配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係Prague會去aeroprague渣下小型飛機，諗緊玩唔玩skydiving<br />\n因為想所有budget控制係10k~12k<br />\n住就搵airbnb<br />\n<br />\n另外仲想問下溝通方面淨係英文會唔會好大障礙，尤其睇牌睇火車站果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為打算巴士/火車去另外兩個城市</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f6f64588eb8467198d590faede4796d82a98a1dd","tid":184033,"uid":102134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T19:49:30.000Z","msg":"布拉格最多玩二,三日<br />\n景點唔多 而且都差唔多<br />\nbtw skydiving 大約千幾蚊 拍片要加10歐定20歐<br />\n<br />\n利申:去過布拉格 覺得好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff1de356d687b09511d69416d3ad1ac22e73be1","tid":184033,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T21:42:14.000Z","msg":"布拉格去2，3日 好好玩wo<br />\nD野食啤酒平到...<br />\n人在布拉格 前日去左CK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6227fd1bbda03a58fe758af872b2fd4f126d88d1","tid":184033,"uid":27334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:18:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>布拉格最多玩二,三日<br />\n景點唔多 而且都差唔多<br />\nbtw skydiving 大約千幾蚊 拍片要加10歐定20歐<br />\n<br />\n利申:去過布拉格 覺得好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跳+片235歐<br />\n小型飛機就190歐一個package<br />\n如果2-3日就夠係咪應該可以去多幾個城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身驚14日去Vienna+Budapest會唔夠<br />\n上網睇過prague物價同香港差唔多係咪真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9376f69110e3734efa01788eb09355aea8ad1731","tid":184033,"uid":27334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:18:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>布拉格去2，3日 好好玩wo<br />\nD野食啤酒平到...<br />\n人在布拉格 前日去左CK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCK係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f566e596aa520da0934533043d8cedff2bbffa73","tid":184033,"uid":80909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T18:55:53.000Z","msg":"budapest幾正 幾值得去 <br />\n物價低而且建築夜景都好靚<br />\nCK係捷克一個小鎮 可以係布拉格一日來回<br />\n或者去CK再直落奧地利Hallstatt<br />\n睇你想食玩shopping定想睇靚景"},{"pid":"0f7537e09b69916d402179ff9916488c76763a01","tid":184033,"uid":80909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T18:57:36.000Z","msg":"vienna就真係除非你好想聽opera啦<br />\n我本身唔好藝術呢家野 冇聽opera<br />\n所以去一日都覺得悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b521916bff97cddef4ae6dd57b776586e1ad1103","tid":184033,"uid":27334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T05:25:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>vienna就真係除非你好想聽opera啦<br />\n我本身唔好藝術呢家野 冇聽opera<br />\n所以去一日都覺得悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nThanks 絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見paris機票平 2千8左右所以又想去左paris兩三日先之後去Prague&gt;Vienna&gt;Budapest<br />\n唔知夠唔夠時間<br />\n聽你咁講有可能會skip左Vienna<br />\n<br />\n我就係想睇景多過shopping<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2604098a25a5fd940b71e78ed1a3b07b4db866f","tid":184033,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T07:07:54.000Z","msg":"Prague &gt; ck &gt; Hallstatt &gt; Salzburg &gt; konigssee &gt; salZburg  &gt; Budapest <br />\n時間剛剛好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b1999812083cfac0649a53fd3e87f375082e57f","tid":184033,"uid":27334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:10:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Prague &gt; ck &gt; Hallstatt &gt; Salzburg &gt; konigssee &gt; salZburg  &gt; Budapest <br />\n時間剛剛好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打，每個point suggest留幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外我有另一個plan<br />\nHKG&gt;Paris $2800 <br />\nParis&gt;Prague $350<br />\nPrague陸路去Budapest<br />\n然後Budapest&gt;Paris $350&gt;HKG<br />\n咁樣加埋仲平過來回prague仲可以去多個地方<br />\n建唔建議咁做？小弟想控制係10k內去14日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 是否太大撚頭 同埋呢條route唔知去唔去到Ck同Hallstatt"},{"pid":"db04cf037edf876a17ed5e445b92c1bccea05f9f","tid":184033,"uid":17052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:18:16.000Z","msg":"Austria 同Czech 都可以挑機唔買地鐵飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 而家係salzburg等緊上機"},{"pid":"fb2ba3e257cbaca66e611dfb0ead8332a00ff3a9","tid":184033,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:20:46.000Z","msg":"以為你要去十四日布拉格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n揸埋小型飛機budget都仲可以係12k內?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nprague同budapest都住過airbnb, 係平靚正既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad742fd3852c7ae06793124fd1374c48c1923a5b","tid":184033,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:22:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Prague &gt; ck &gt; Hallstatt &gt; Salzburg &gt; konigssee &gt; salZburg  &gt; Budapest <br />\n時間剛剛好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打，每個point suggest留幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外我有另一個plan<br />\nHKG&gt;Paris $2800 <br />\nParis&gt;Prague $350<br />\nPrague陸路去Budapest<br />\n然後Budapest&gt;Paris $350&gt;HKG<br />\n咁樣加埋仲平過來回prague仲可以去多個地方<br />\n建唔建議咁做？小弟想控制係10k內去14日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 是否太大撚頭 同埋呢條route唔知去唔去到Ck同Hallstatt</blockquote><br />\n點解要加巴黎落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩條線先剛剛夠玩<br />\n試下 Prg bud 咁試下買機票 或 vie <br />\n 三者互試，vie 機場有車直去二邊，布拉格約4小時，布達佩斯就一小時"},{"pid":"c43f84261867fd9064c068afd9149b89ecb1f610","tid":184033,"uid":27334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:24:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為你要去十四日布拉格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n揸埋小型飛機budget都仲可以係12k內?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nprague同budapest都住過airbnb, 係平靚正既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小型飛機有個package 190歐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4f7d7463f1e7d71bf8e3643e92afc71d989ff7","tid":184033,"uid":27334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:25:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Prague &gt; ck &gt; Hallstatt &gt; Salzburg &gt; konigssee &gt; salZburg  &gt; Budapest <br />\n時間剛剛好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打，每個point suggest留幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外我有另一個plan<br />\nHKG&gt;Paris $2800 <br />\nParis&gt;Prague $350<br />\nPrague陸路去Budapest<br />\n然後Budapest&gt;Paris $350&gt;HKG<br />\n咁樣加埋仲平過來回prague仲可以去多個地方<br />\n建唔建議咁做？小弟想控制係10k內去14日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 是否太大撚頭 同埋呢條route唔知去唔去到Ck同Hallstatt</blockquote><br />\n點解要加巴黎落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩條線先剛剛夠玩<br />\n試下 Prg bud 咁試下買機票 或 vie <br />\n 三者互試，vie 機場有車直去二邊，布拉格約4小時，布達佩斯就一小時</blockquote><br />\n我都覺硬係怪怪地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 純粹見好似平啲既玩法但應該chur chur地<br />\n不過岩岩睇salzburg火車同飛機都唔平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81b1841d4f2206ddf258c80a8a4fb870e7dc671","tid":184033,"uid":27334,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:26:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Austria 同Czech 都可以挑機唔買地鐵飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 而家係salzburg等緊上機</blockquote><br />\n絲打SZG去PRG?"},{"pid":"58899db4d4a5191eddafe704ec82446cafaa728b","tid":184033,"uid":27334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:32:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a24f9fbf875229416da3fade22eabb3dc3987152","tid":184033,"uid":17052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T11:49:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Austria 同Czech 都可以挑機唔買地鐵飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 而家係salzburg等緊上機</blockquote><br />\n絲打SZG去PRG?</blockquote><br />\n我Salzburg 返London <br />\nPrague CK CB Vienna Linz Salzburg Hallstatt<br />\n都可以問我 雖然未必啱哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"